OL,6,FThe head of Hospitality Association is
OL,7,Fcalling for an independent review into
OL,8,Fthe Bailiwick's air links.
OL,10,FAlan Sillett says tourism will be
OL,11,Fseverely hampered unless something
OL,12,Fchanges, with some tickets for the
OL,13,Fgovernment-owned airline Aurigny
OL,14,Fcosting more than #200 each way.
OL,16,FTheir arrangement states the company
OL,17,Fwill "forsake a profit motive beyond
OL,18,Fthat needed to be financially self-
OL,19,Fsufficient in favour of affordable air
OL,20,Ftravel".
