OL,4,Cexpensive' cost of flights
OL,6,FMr Sillett added: "If that current
OL,7,Fagreement between the States of
OL,8,FGuernsey and the state airline isn't
OL,9,Fworking for the island, then there
OL,10,Fneeds to be some expertise brought in
OL,11,Fto find a better way forward."
OL,13,FThe President of the States Trading
OL,14,FSupervisory Board which oversees
OL,15,FGuernsey Airport, Deputy Peter Roffey,
OL,16,Fhas admitted the cost of some tickets
OL,17,Fis "uber expensive" but explained the
OL,18,Fdifficulties of changing the pricing
OL,19,Fmodel.
