OL,3,CCall for independent review into 'uber
OL,4,Cexpensive' cost of flights
OL,6,FHe said: "We could ask Aurigny to have
OL,7,Fa far flatter fare structure, but
OL,8,Fthat's a double-edged sword. You would
OL,9,Fnot get these uber-expensive fares for
OL,10,Fthe last few seats but those people
OL,11,Fbooking early, the Guernsey person
OL,12,Ftypically wanting to go on holiday,
OL,13,Fwouldn't get the #69-pound flights
OL,14,Fthey're getting at the moment.
OL,16,F"They would have to be far higher so I
OL,17,Fthink you have to be careful what you
OL,18,Fask for."
