OL,6,FPassengers at Guernsey Airport shared
OL,7,Fmixed views on the fares as some
OL,8,Fcriticised them for being too
OL,9,Fexpensive, whilst others said they
OL,10,Fthought their trip was good value for
OL,11,Fmoney.
OL,13,FAurigny defended its prices, saying
OL,14,Fthe highlighted costs give a skewed
OL,15,Fview.
