OL,6,FIt stated: "The data point which the
OL,7,FGuernsey Hospitality Association has
OL,8,Fchosen to highlight is outbound prices
OL,9,Ffrom next week, 18 March. This is just
OL,10,Fbefore the school Easter break, a very
OL,11,Fpopular time for customers to book for
OL,12,Fthe London Gatwick route.
OL,14,F"As this is less than two weeks away,
OL,15,Fit is not surprising that two flights
OL,16,Fthat day are already sold out and the
OL,17,Fincrease in demand understandably
OL,18,Fimpacts the prices of remaining seats.
